\sin3A+\cos3A=\sin2A(\cos A-\sin A)+\cos2A(\cos A+\sin A)
\sin2A=2\sin A\cos A
\cos2A(\cos A+\sin A)=(\cos^2A-\sin^2A)(\cos A+\sin A)=(\cos A-\sin A)(\cos A+\sin A)^2=(\cos A-\sin A)(1+\sin2A)
\sin3A=3\sin A-4\sin^3A,\cos3A=4\cos^3A-3\cos A
\sin3A+\cos3A=3\sin A-4\sin^3A+4\cos^3A-3\cos A=3(\sin A-\cos A)-4(\sin^3A-\cos^3A)
\displaystyle\sin^3A-\cos^3A=(\sin A-\cos A)(\sin^2A+\sin A\cos A+\cos^2A)=(\sin A-\cos A)\left(1+\frac{\sin2A}2\right)
